  section.feature-group
      .feature-group__heading
        .l
          h3.title
            | Organize your world—in a customizable way.
          p.
            A system as unique as your challenges: Transpose lets you create, 
            organize, and search in your own way.<br>
            Roll over a section to learn more about Transpose’s features.

      .feature-group__inner
        .l
          ul.feature-group__cards
            li.card
              strong.card__title
                | Create
              .card__flipper
