                  .card__icon
                    i.icon.icon-bulb
                  p.
                    Transpose is the simplest way to capture and build what matters to you.
                    And it's flexible enough for projects <br> big and small.
                  footer.card__footer
                    span Roll over to learn more
                
                .card__back
                  .card__icon-small
                    i.icon.icon-bulb
