                  p.
                    <b>Intelligent.</b> Our system works for you behind the scenes, 
                    analyzing items to make them easy to find.
                  p.
                    <b>Search different formats with ease.</b> 
                    Transpose recognizes all kinds of files—even voice recordings 
                    and images—so you can search through them like text.

            li.card
